PROJECT NAME:
Beneficiary Records Management System (PWA)

PROJECT PURPOSE:
A mobile-first Progressive Web Application for government office personnel to search and view beneficiary records.

SYSTEM TYPE:
View-Only Information System

USERS:

* Approximately 25 authorized users
* Mobile phone users
* Android
* iPhone
* Tablet

DATA SOURCE:
Google Sheets (Master Data)

DATABASE:
Supabase PostgreSQL

AUTHENTICATION:
Supabase Auth (Email + Password)

SYNC:
Google Sheets → Google Apps Script → Supabase

CURRENT STATUS:
Google Sheets sync is working.
Supabase contains 872 beneficiary records.
Authentication is working.
Dashboard is working.
Records page is working.
Details page is working.

